--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
selkie-rs
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

studio renders Mermaid diagrams via `selkie-rs`, a fork of selkie by btucker
(https://github.com/btucker/selkie), used under the MIT License (above).

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SQLite
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Windows-API knowledge database (`windows_api.db`) is read through SQLite,
embedded via the `libsqlite3-sys` "bundled" feature. SQLite is in the public
domain; the authors disclaim copyright. See https://www.sqlite.org/copyright.html.

